              </svg>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm sm:text-base">100% Open Source</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3 sm:mb-4">Community-driven development. Contribute, fork, and customize. MIT Licensed.</p>
            <a href="https://github.com/spaquet/listopia" target="_blank" class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-purple-600 font-medium hover:text-purple-700">→ View Repository</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>